node.text: of #TheConversation with @masikakalysha and @hazelebaby takes place only on @thezeusnetwork! Tune in THIS Sunday at 5pm PST/8pm EST!! Executive Produced by ME and @rayj - Click the link in bio to subscribe and tune in!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Princess Love Norwood on September 05, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text:
Had an amazing time celebrating 10 years of marriage for one of my favorite couples @bellaneri3 and @therealnoreaga 💫

The love you two share is undeniable and unconditional. Cheers to eternal LOVE 🥂❤️ YALLA 🥳🎉

Shoutout to my bestie @jtavar_ it’s always a 🎥 when we link up (P.S. 2nd slide was when I kept accidentally poking him in the eye 😂)
